data.description: This Amazing Home out in the country Perfect for your Family. Lots of Updates and Large yard for the Kids ! Home Features Generac Backup Generator, Above Ground Pool and Lots of parking. Large Family Room with Fireplace and large Master Bedroom and Beautiful Walk in Shower with a Seat & Nice Walk in large Closet, Kitchen Feature Corian Countertops and Stainless Steel Refrigerator and Dishwasher. Just 3 miles from Remington. 1 year old Storage Building with Overhead Door. Concrete Storage Building in backyard Yard. Home has a Huge Magnolia Tree and lots of shades. Home features a Nice Dining Room and another Large Family / Den Room. Yard Also has Nice Dog Pen with 2 dog Houses for your Pets. Home surrounded by Farmers Fields so neighbors are not close ! also Features a Garage and Carport. Call Me Today to Make a Appt See agent Remarks. **Fema Flood Zone X Moderate**
